Pressly Hart Birthday: December 1 , 1988 (33 years)Very pretty and petite 5’3″ brunette Presley Hart was born on December 1, 1988 in Norco, California. She’s the middle child in a family of three daughters. Hart moved around frequently while growing up and spent a lot of time in Colorado, where her father was in the Navy.
